column5: Hi Guys/girls could anyone tell me the date for 2009 fishing for Tyler day?, Lures and Tours is including this event on their calender which is going to press very soon.  Thanks!  Mark

here is a  cut and paste from the tyler thread "This year it will be held on Sat. Feb 14. I realize it's Valentines day, but it's also the license free weekend thumbsup_anim.gif . As usual things will begin at 7am and measurements at 1 I think, plenty of time to get everyone home in time to be with their honies "
You can also PM Maureen for additional information.
